fulltitle: Jazz Theory with Barry Harris, Part Two
uploader: Jazz at Lincoln Center's JAZZ ACADEMY
channel: Jazz at Lincoln Center's JAZZ ACADEMY
description:
Sit down with the legendary Barry Harris for a piano and theory lesson that will expand your harmonic vocabulary and give you deeper insight into the music!

Learn more at the Jazz Academy by visiting http://academy.jalc.org

Barry Harris - Piano
Eli Yamin - Piano
Eric Suquet - Director
Bill Thomas - Director of Photography
Aaron Chandler - Audio Engineer
Richard Emery - Production Assistant
Seton Hawkins - Producer

Recorded September 11, 2013
